#### HTML Code

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Parcel Retention Notification</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic styling for a clean and modern look */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

       .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

       .header {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

       .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666666;
        }

       .call-to-action {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

       .call-to-action:hover {
            background-color: #3e8e41;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            Parcel Retention Notification
        </div>
        <div class="message">
            Dear [Recipient's Name],
            <br><br>
            We regret to inform you that your parcel has been retained due to outstanding payments. Please find the details below:
            <br><br>
            <table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                    <td>Parcel Reference:</td>
                    <td>[Parcel Reference]</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Outstanding Amount:</td>
                    <td>[Outstanding Amount]</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <br><br>
            To resolve this issue, please complete the payment by clicking the link below:
            <br><br>
            <a href="[Payment Link]" class="call-to-action">Complete Payment</a>
            <br><br>
            If you have already made the payment, please contact our customer support team at [Customer Support Email] for further assistance.
            <br><br>
            Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.
            <br><br>
            Best regards,
            <br>
            [Your Name]
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

#### Example Use Case

To use this HTML code, simply replace the placeholders with the actual values:

* `[Recipient's Name]`: The name of the recipient.
* `[Parcel Reference]`: The reference number of the parcel.
* `[Outstanding Amount]`: The amount that is outstanding.
* `[Payment Link]`: The link to the payment portal.
* `[Customer Support Email]`: The email address of the customer support team.
* `[Your Name]`: Your name.

Then, copy and paste the code into an HTML email template, and send it to the recipient.

